---
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 bg-[#fcfbf8]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 font-serif tracking-tight">
        The Three Pillars of Local Dominance
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-sans">
        We don't do generic SEO. We execute a proven playbook designed specifically for local service businesses to monopolize their area.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-24">
      
      <!-- Pillar 1 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mb-6">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Show up first when locals search for your service.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg">
            When someone searches "[your service] near me," Google shows 3 businesses on the map. If you're not in those top 3, you're invisible. We get you there and keep you there.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Full Google Business Profile optimisation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>50+ directory listings across the web</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Ongoing Maps ranking management across your whole service area</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <img src="/images/v4-maps-proof.jpg" alt="Google Maps Ranking Proof" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 2 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <img src="/images/v4-hero-proof.jpg" alt="Google Search Ranking Proof" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mb-6">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Your business on Page 1 — not your competitors.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg">
            Organic traffic that comes to you every day without spending a cent on ads. We build pages that Google loves and customers trust.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>SEO-optimised pages targeting the exact words your customers type</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Technical fixes to make your site lightning fast</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Suburb expansion as your rankings grow</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 3 -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mb-6">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Build a wall of 5-star reviews — without lifting a finger.</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg">
            More reviews means more trust means more calls. You become the obvious choice before anyone even picks up the phone.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Automated review requests after every job</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Happy customers go to Google, concerns go to a private form</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              <span>Every review gets a professional response</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <img src="/images/v4-review-proof.jpg" alt="5-Star Reviews Proof" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <a 
        href="https://calendar.app.google/ceK9b3Jr3KGD9cCs5" 
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex h-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-900 px-8 text-base font-medium text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-all"
      >
        Book Your Strategy Session
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
